trans-unit.source: Represents the configuration section that contains a list of behaviors that is applied to all [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] services on the machine before the behaviors in the <xref uid="langword_csharp_behaviors" name="behaviors" href=""></xref> section are applied.
trans-unit.target: Representerar konfigurationsavsnittet som innehåller en lista över beteenden som tillämpas på alla [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] tjänster på datorn innan beteenden i den <xref uid="langword_csharp_behaviors" name="behaviors" href=""> </xref> avsnittet tillämpas.

trans-unit.source: This configuration section is defined in the Machine.config file.
It contains a list of behaviors that is applied to all [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] services on the machine before the behaviors in the `behaviors` section are applied.
trans-unit.target: Den innehåller en lista över beteenden som tillämpas på alla [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] tjänster på datorn innan beteenden i den `behaviors` avsnittet tillämpas.

trans-unit.source: If a behavior is defined in both sections, the behavior in the `behaviors` sections is given preference.
trans-unit.target: Om ett problem har definierats i både avsnitten beteende i den `behaviors` avsnitt ges inställningar.
